		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔持矛立即进行破击，造成<span color="#ffe599">41%</span><span>伤害，随后翻身，驾驭着长矛继续冲击，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">47%</span><span>伤害，最多可连续冲击3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔抬起长矛，朝前方的地上猛击，造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，梅兰塔扔起长矛，纵身一跃，在玩家处落下，造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔将长矛朝前方丢出，长矛经过将造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="414" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔进行2段左右划攻击，依次造成<span color="#ffe599">32%,34%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔移至场地中央，并立即召唤2枚天矛，先后造成2次<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
