		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，梅兰塔动用空之权能，将<span color="#ffffbf">玩家拉至自身面前</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="441" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔升至空中，展开1或2扇无思之扉，同时开始蓄力，16s后，将直接<span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>当前角色。使用「小右」控制来避免。<br/>展开窗子的数量为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2</span><span>时，被击落后梅兰塔将失去</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1119" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">梅兰塔升至空中，展开4扇无思之扉，同时开始蓄力，16s后，将直接<span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀全队</span><span>角色。使用「小右」控制来避免。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
